videos.headline: Houston's WR screen goes for 67-yard TD
videos.description: Houston's Clayton Tune throws a screen pass to Tre'von Bradley who turns on the jets and scores a 67-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Houston's WR screen goes for 67-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carothers rushes 17 yards for 2nd TD
videos.description: Navy's Jamale Carothers gets the ball and rushes into daylight, going nearly untouched for a 17-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carothers rushes 17 yards for 2nd TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carothers starts second half with 75-yard TD
videos.description: On the first play from scrimmage in the third quarter, Jamale Carothers breaks through the Houston defense for a 75-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carothers starts second half with 75-yard TD) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carothers hits pay dirt for fourth time
videos.description: Navy's Jamale Carothers continues his huge game by ripping through the Houston defense for a 29-yard touchdown, his fourth of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carothers hits pay dirt for fourth time) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Houston turns 4th-and-9 into 22-yard TD
videos.description: On fourth down, Houston's Clayton Tune rolls out of the pocket and flings the ball to Marquez Stevenson for a 22-yard touchdown.
